 505        /// <summary>
 506        /// Finds the child with the specified browse name.
 507        /// </summary>
 508        protected override BaseInstanceState FindChild(
 509            ISystemContext context,
 510            QualifiedName browseName,
 511            bool createOrReplace,
 512            BaseInstanceState replacement) {
 513            if (QualifiedName.IsNull(browseName)) {
 514                return null;
 515            }
 516
 517            BaseInstanceState instance = null;
 518
 519            switch (browseName.Name) {
 520                case BrowseNames.SimulationActive: {
 521                        if (createOrReplace) {
 522                            if (SimulationActive == null) {
 523                                if (replacement == null) {
 524                                    SimulationActive = new PropertyState<bool>(this);
 525                                }
 526                                else {
 527                                    SimulationActive = (PropertyState<bool>)replacement;
 528                                }
 529                            }
 530                        }
 531
 532                        instance = SimulationActive;
 533                        break;
 534                    }
 535
 536                case BrowseNames.GenerateValues: {
 537                        if (createOrReplace) {
 538                            if (GenerateValues == null) {
 539                                if (replacement == null) {
 540                                    GenerateValues = new GenerateValuesMethodState(this);
 541                                }
 542                                else {
 543                                    GenerateValues = (GenerateValuesMethodState)replacement;
 544                                }
 545                            }
 546                        }
 547
 548                        instance = GenerateValues;
 549                        break;
 550                    }
 551
 552                case BrowseNames.CycleComplete: {
 553                        if (createOrReplace) {
 554                            if (CycleComplete == null) {
 555                                if (replacement == null) {
 556                                    CycleComplete = new AcknowledgeableConditionState(this);
 557                                }
 558                                else {
 559                                    CycleComplete = (AcknowledgeableConditionState)replacement;
 560                                }
 561                            }
 562                        }
 563
 564                        instance = CycleComplete;
 565                        break;
 566                    }
 567            }
 568
 569            if (instance != null) {
 570                return instance;
 571            }
 572
 573            return base.FindChild(context, browseName, createOrReplace, replacement);
 574        }
